data.description: Explore this two-story, 5-bedroom home with an additional loft upstairs and a media room, nestled in West San Antonio. The bright and spacious modern interior is accented with designer finishes throughout. The grand chef's kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances and a large granite island with bar seating, is perfect for culinary creations and casual gatherings. The primary bedroom is located downstairs with a large walk-in shower, double vanity and spacious closet. You will find a guest bedroom downstairs with its own bathroom. The downstairs secondary bedroom can also be used as a study/office space. Upstairs, the open loft area offers extra space for entertainment or relaxation, adding to the home's luxurious feel. Equipped with a media room and 3 additional bedrooms upstairs, this home has is all! Each room provides ample space, ensuring comfort and a personalized retreat for all. The well-landscaped backyard, a focus of the sellers' investment, features an extended deck with storage space below and a gated dog run connecting to the doggie door navigating into the airconditioned garage, creating an ideal setting for relaxation and play. This home is more than just a living space; it's an experience of comfort and luxury, perfectly situated to enjoy the best of West San Antonio, close to shopping, dining, Lackland AFB and SeaWorld.
